column4: Motorists can expect delays this afternoon due to traffic signals dark and trees down in several sections of Lexington.
Alexandria Dr at Old Frankfort Pike.
Alumni Dr at Turkey Foot Rd.
Outbound Tates Creek Rd at Albany Rd
Man O War Blvd - various intersections between Alumni Dr and I-75.
Richmond Rd - various intersections between N Eagle Creek Dr and Hays Blvd.
Harrodsburg Rd at Corporate Dr and Ft Harrods Dr.
New Circle Rd at Liberty Rd.
